The First ever edition of RADL GRVL brought us to the stunning Mclaren Vale Wine region and beautiful Adelaide, Australian hills! With perfect weather and amazing people along the ride we conquered the 108km race and had some fun along the way! Thanks to @CanyonBicycles for an amazing event!

